Wikimania
[[Image:Jimbosmom.jpg|thumb|Everyone gets a turn with Jimbo's mom at Wikimania]]


'''Wikimania''' is a convention where [[pedophiles]] get together and molest children.  It is hosted by notorious child molester, Jimbo Wales.  The next Wikimania will be held August 26 to 28 in Argentina.  Here the new administrators are forced to swear loyalty to [[NAMBLA]] and then an orgy of young boy sex occurs.  Jimbo Wales usually leads his minons in satanic rituals and then they all have gay sex again.

